Package data.problem

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Configuration
    The configuration class will hold the important information to be passed to the specified algorithm The valueArray type works by not having a restriction in what value you put it, any object type is valid.
    Problem
    The class problem will be the operational class given by the user, made from the submission.
    ProblemFitnessApp
    This class will contain the app to evaluate the configuration sent by the user.
    ProblemInputs
    ProblemInputs will contain the inputs for the problem.
    ProblemIntroduction
    This class will hold basic information about the problem, such as its defining name or the email from the user.
    ProblemOptimization
    This class will contain the list of @see Algorithm to run using the given configuration lists by the client.
    Restriction
    This class will define specific restriction the user wants applied to the algorithms run.
